### ADR 001: Konva Migration (2025-11-04)
- **Datei**: [001-konva-migration.md](decisions/001-konva-migration.md)
- **Status**: ‚úÖ Accepted & Implemented
- **Typ**: Technology
- **Impact**: High
- **Summary**: Migration von Phaser.js zu Konva.js
  - 72% Bundle-Reduktion (600KB ‚Üí 165KB)
  - 66% Code-Reduktion
  - 90% Drag & Drop Vereinfachung

